<div class="news">
	<h3><a href="/zpravicky/fb-tb-a-roztrzeny-pytel/">FB, TB a roztržený pytel</a></h3>

	<div>A jakoby se nám s release candidate verzemi roztrhl pytel, včera byli na <a href="http://www.mozillazine.org/talkback.html?article=3753" title="Mozilla Firebird 0.7 and Mozilla Thunderbird 0.3 Release Candidates">MozillaZine</a> oznámeni <a href="http://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/firebird/nightly/latest-0.7/">Mozilla Firebird 0.7 rc</a> a <a href="http://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/thunderbird/nightly/2003-09-24-1.5/">Mozilla Thunderbird 0.3 rc2</a>.</div>
